(@categoryID3, N'Premium Laptops', N'Premium laptops feature luxurious designs, high-quality materials, and powerful configurations. They are often equipped with the latest processors, high-resolution displays, impressive battery life, and modern features like fingerprint sensors, touchscreens, or premium audio. Suitable for executives, professionals, and those demanding top-tier performance and style.', 1),
(@categoryID4, N'MacBook', N'MacBooks are laptops produced by Apple, renowned for their sleek, sophisticated design and stable performance. Running on macOS, they offer a smooth, secure experience optimized for the Apple ecosystem. Equipped with sharp Retina displays and impressive battery life, they are optimized for creative work like graphic design, video editing, and programming. A popular choice for professionals and students alike.', 1);

